import { Container, Row, Image, Col, Card, InputGroup, Form } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { MdEmail } from 'react-icons/md';
import React from 'react'

class Login extends React.Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Container className='h-100 align-middle'>
                <Row className='h-100'>
                    <Col className='m-auto img_login p-0'>
                        <Image className='w-100  ' src="https://colorlib.com/etc/lf/Login_v18/images/bg-01.jpg" rounded></Image>
                    </Col>
                    <Col className='m-auto p-0'>
                        <Card className='m-auto'>
                            <Card.Body>
                                <Card.Title>Đăng nhập</Card.Title>
                                <Card.Subtitle className="mb-2 text-muted">Welcome back, Vui lòng đăng nhập đến tài khoản của bạn</Card.Subtitle>
                                <Form>
                                    <Form.Group controlId="formBasicEmail">
                                        <Form.Label>Email address</Form.Label>
                                        <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="Enter email" />
                                        <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                                            We'll never share your email with anyone else.
    </Form.Text>
                                    </Form.Group>

                                    <Form.Group controlId="formBasicPassword">
                                        <Form.Label>Password</Form.Label>
                                        <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="Password" />
                                    </Form.Group>
                                    <Form.Group controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
                                        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" />
                                    </Form.Group>
                                    <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                                        Submit
  </Button>
                                </Form>
                            </Card.Body>
                        </Card>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        )
    }
}
export default Login;
